Class Deck<C extends ICard>

  • java.lang.Object

  • Type Parameters:
    C - the subclass of ICard to be used.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    ICardset<C>, IDeck<C>, ListenableCardset<C>, java.lang.Iterable<C>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Deck
    public abstract class Deck<C extends ICard>
extends Cardset<C>
implements IDeck<C>
    A base deck object for a card game.

    Subclasses will need to implement the methods required by the IDeck interface. Since this generic version is unable to construct the generic type ICards.
